---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Programming</h2>
		<p>Assembly Language, Basic, Arduino C++, Forth, Excel Macros, Sql Server, JavaScript, JAVA, Google Apps, C#, Python/Tkinter, HTML/CSS, Astro, , micro processor devices.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="moon-stars" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Artist</h2>
		<p>Metal art with, and without, a metal lathe, wood carving, jewelry making, pyrography (wood burning), carved tree.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="pencil-line" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Writer</h2>
		<p>Published 16 articles from 1979 to 1984 and one in 1995 in computer magazines (1 British), 5 articles in computer books from 1977 to 1981. Also wrote my memoirs and <em>The Women in my Life</em> (both not published, but are in hand made books), and <b><em>Stories and Poems of the Good and the Horrible</em></b> on Amazon</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
